products.title: Corsica, Mauve - Roman Blind
products.metadescription: Corsica, mauve - roman blind the light mauve and apple green of the corsica mauve are a summer dream come true, with a pretty pattern of florals and foliage interwoven with each other across a soft white canvas. The look will work as part of either a cont
products.productdescription: The light mauve and apple green of the corsica mauve are a summer dream come true, with a pretty pattern of florals and foliage interwoven with each other across a soft white canvas. The look will work as part of either a contemporary or traditional dcor scheme.Use the mauve to add some gentle colour to your bathroom, where it will look stunning against a white bathroom suite and tiling. Accent with towels and accessories in matching greens and lilacs.Please note: roman blinds over 130cm wide require vertical seams due to limited fabric width. We recommended you split large windows into smaller blinds.

products.title: Corsica, Gold - Roman Blind
products.metadescription: Corsica, gold - roman blind the corsica range is one filled with class and sophistication, without giving up its traditional floral roots. The gold offers this pretty floral pattern in a golden yellow and parchment grey, resulting in a stunningly understa
products.productdescription: The corsica range is one filled with class and sophistication, without giving up its traditional floral roots. The gold offers this pretty floral pattern in a golden yellow and parchment grey, resulting in a stunningly understated feel all over.Give the gold a home in your living room or guest bedroom, where the subtle yellow tone will add a hint of cheer without overwhelming the room. Surround with greys and similar shades of yellow for a coordinated look, opting for silver fittings and fixtures, and perhaps the occasional ornament or oddment.Please note: roman blinds over 130cm wide require vertical seams due to limited fabric width. We recommended you split large windows into smaller blinds.
